# Google Calendar busy-time OAuth (SPA / public client id only).
#
# To pick Google Calendar events as busy times, create an OAuth Web Client ID,
# enable the Calendar API for that project, then set GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID below.
# Add your dev origin (for example http://localhost:5173) under Authorized
# JavaScript origins. Keep GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET server-side only — this app
# uses the public client id and does not bundle the secret.

GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
